#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="167"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.6.2" href="#Bu-Pj.4.6.2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.700" href="#ms.700"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.1"
msgid "Tīhākārehi … pe … sattahākārehi yo te cīvaraṃ paribhuñji …"
msgstr "If he lies in full awareness, saying, “The monk who made use of your robes …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.2"
msgid "yo te piṇḍapātaṃ paribhuñji …"
msgstr "who made use of your almsfood …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.3"
msgid "yo te senāsanaṃ paribhuñji …"
msgstr "who made use of your lodging requisites …"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.171" href="#bd.1.171"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.4"
msgid "yo te gilā­nappac­caya­bhesaj­ja­parik­khā­raṃ paribhuñji"
msgstr "who made use of your medicines"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.5"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji …"
msgstr "attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.6"
msgid "samāpajjati …"
msgstr "is attaining …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.7"
msgid "samāpanno …"
msgstr "has attained …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.8"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī …"
msgstr "obtains …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.9"
msgid "vasī …"
msgstr "masters …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.10"
msgid "tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatanti sampajānamusā bhaṇantassa paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti thullaccayassa;"
msgstr "has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” then, if the listener understands, he commits a serious offense when three conditions are fulfilled;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.11"
msgid "na paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "if the listener does not understand, he commits an offense of wrong conduct when three conditions are fulfilled … when seven conditions are fulfilled …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:171.12"
msgid "vinidhāya bhāvaṃ."
msgstr "he misrepresents his sentiment of what is true."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="168"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.701" href="#ms.701"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.1"
msgid "Tīhākārehi … pe … sattahākārehi yena te vihāro paribhutto …"
msgstr "If he lies in full awareness, saying, “The monk who has made use of your dwelling …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.2"
msgid "yena te cīvaraṃ paribhuttaṃ …"
msgstr "who has made use of your robes …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.3"
msgid "yena te piṇḍapāto paribhutto …"
msgstr "who has made use of your almsfood …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.4"
msgid "yena te senāsanaṃ paribhuttaṃ …"
msgstr "who has made use of your lodging requisites …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.5"
msgid "yena te gilā­nappac­caya­bhesaj­ja­parik­khāro paribhutto …"
msgstr "who has made use of your medicines"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.6"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji …"
msgstr "attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.7"
msgid "samāpajjati …"
msgstr "is attaining …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.8"
msgid "samāpanno …"
msgstr "has attained …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.9"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī …"
msgstr "obtains …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.10"
msgid "vasī …"
msgstr "masters …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.11"
msgid "tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatanti sampajānamusā bhaṇantassa paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti thullaccayassa;"
msgstr "has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” then, if the listener understands, he commits a serious offense when three conditions are fulfilled;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.12"
msgid "na paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr "if the listener does not understand, he commits an offense of wrong conduct when three conditions are fulfilled … when seven conditions are fulfilled …"

#. <span class="note" hidden>The Pali has an additional set of ellipses points between “who has made use of your medicines” and “attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling.” This seems to be a mistake.</span> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:172.13"
msgid "vinidhāya bhāvaṃ."
msgstr "he misrepresents his sentiment of what is true."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="169"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.702" href="#ms.702"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.1"
msgid "Tīhākārehi … pe … sattahākārehi yaṃ tvaṃ āgamma vihāraṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "If he lies in full awareness, saying, “The monk to whom you gave a dwelling …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.2"
msgid "cīvaraṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "to whom you gave robes …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.3"
msgid "piṇḍapātaṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "to whom you gave almsfood …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.4"
msgid "senāsanaṃ adāsi …"
msgstr "to whom you gave lodging requisites …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.5"
msgid "gilā­nappac­caya­bhesaj­ja­parik­khā­raṃ adāsi"
msgstr "to whom you gave medicines"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.6"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji …"
msgstr "he attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.7"
msgid "samāpajjati …"
msgstr "is attaining …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.8"
msgid "samāpanno …"
msgstr "has attained …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.9"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī …"
msgstr "obtains …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.10"
msgid "vasī …"
msgstr "masters …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.11"
msgid "tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatanti sampajānamusā bhaṇantassa paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti thullaccayassa;"
msgstr "has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” then, if the listener understands, he commits a serious offense when three conditions are fulfilled;"

#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.100" href="#Vin.3.100"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.12"
msgid "na paṭi­vijānan­tassa āpatti dukkaṭassa—"
msgstr "if the listener does not understand, he commits an offense of wrong conduct when three conditions are fulfilled … when seven conditions are fulfilled:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.13"
msgid "pubbevassa hoti musā bhaṇissanti,"
msgstr "before he has lied, he knows he is going to lie;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.14"
msgid "bhaṇantassa hoti musā bhaṇāmīti,"
msgstr "while lying, he knows he is lying;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.15"
msgid "bhaṇitassa hoti musā mayā bhaṇitanti,"
msgstr "after he has lied, he knows he has lied;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.16"
msgid "vinidhāya diṭṭhiṃ,"
msgstr "he misrepresents his view of what is true;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.17"
msgid "vinidhāya khantiṃ,"
msgstr "he misrepresents his belief of what is true;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.18"
msgid "vinidhāya ruciṃ,"
msgstr "he misrepresents his acceptance of what is true;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:173.19"
msgid "vinidhāya bhāvaṃ."
msgstr "he misrepresents his sentiment of what is true."

#. </p><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="170"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.703" href="#ms.703"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:174.1"
msgid "Peyyā­la­panna­rasa­kaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The successive fifteen are finished."

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:174.2"
msgid "Pac­ca­yap­paṭi­saṃ­yutta­vāraka­thā niṭṭhitā."
msgstr "The exposition of the section on that connected with requisites is finished."

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:174.3"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhamma­cakka­peyyā­laṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The successive permutation series on super-human qualities is finished."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="171"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.7" href="#Bu-Pj.4.7.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.704" href="#ms.704"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.2"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.3"
msgid "adhimānena,"
msgstr "if he overestimates himself;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.4"
msgid "anul­lapa­nādhip­pāyassa,"
msgstr "if he does not intend to make a claim;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.5"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.6"
msgid "khittacittassa,"
msgstr "if he is deranged;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.7"
msgid "vedanāṭṭassa,"
msgstr "if he is overwhelmed by pain;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:175.8"
msgid "ādi­kammi­kas­sāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:176.1"
msgid "4.1. Vinīta­vatthu­uddāna­gāthā"
msgstr "Case rulings"

#. </h2><div class="uddana"><h5>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:176.2"
msgid ""
msgstr "Mnemonic list"

#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="172"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.705" href="#ms.705"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:177.1"
msgid "Adhimāne araññamhi,"
msgstr "About overestimation, in the wilderness,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:177.2"
msgid "piṇ­ḍo­paj­jhāriyā­patho;"
msgstr "Almsfood, a preceptor, behavior;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:177.3"
msgid "Saṃyojanā rahodhammā,"
msgstr "Fetters, qualities in private,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:177.4"
msgid "vihāro paccupaṭṭhito."
msgstr "A dwelling, attended on."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="173"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.706" href="#ms.706"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:178.1"
msgid "Na dukkaraṃ viriyamathopi maccuno,"
msgstr "Not difficult, energy, fear of death,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:178.2"
msgid "Bhāyāvuso vippaṭisāri sammā;"
msgstr "Remorseful friend, rightly;"

#. <br><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.172" href="#bd.1.172"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:178.3"
msgid "Viriyena yogena ārādhanāya,"
msgstr "By energy, by exertion,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:178.4"
msgid "Atha vedanāya adhivāsanā duve."
msgstr "Two on the enduring of feeling."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="174"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.707" href="#ms.707"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:179.1"
msgid "Brāhmaṇe pañca vatthūni,"
msgstr "Five stories on a brahmin,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:179.2"
msgid "aññaṃ byākaraṇā tayo;"
msgstr "Three on declaring final knowledge;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:179.3"
msgid "Agārāvaraṇā kāmā,"
msgstr "House, rejected sense-pleasures,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:179.4"
msgid "rati cāpi apakkami."
msgstr "And delight, set out."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="175"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.708" href="#ms.708"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:180.1"
msgid "Aṭṭhi pesi ubho gāvaghātakā,"
msgstr "Bone, lump: both are cattle-butchers,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:180.2"
msgid "Piṇḍo sākuṇiko nicchavi orabbhi;"
msgstr "A morsel is a poultry-butcher, a sheep-butcher is flayed;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:180.3"
msgid "Asi ca sūkariko satti māgavi,"
msgstr "And a pig-butcher and sword, a deer-hunter and knife,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:180.4"
msgid "Usu ca kāraṇiko sūci sārathi."
msgstr "And a torturer and arrow, a horse trainer and needle."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="176"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.709" href="#ms.709"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:181.1"
msgid "Yo ca sibbīyati sūcako hi so,"
msgstr "And a slanderer is sewn,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:181.2"
msgid "Aṇḍabhāri ahu gāmakūṭako;"
msgstr "A corrupt magistrate with testicles as burden;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:181.3"
msgid "Kūpe nimuggo hi so pāradāriko,"
msgstr "An adulterer submerged in a pit,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:181.4"
msgid "Gūthakhādī ahu duṭṭhabrāhmaṇo."
msgstr "An eater of dung was a wicked brahmin."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="177"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.710" href="#ms.710"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:182.1"
msgid "Nicchavitthī aticārinī ahu,"
msgstr "A flayed woman was an adulteress,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:182.2"
msgid "Maṅgulitthī ahu ikkhaṇitthikā;"
msgstr "An ugly woman was a fortune-teller;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:182.3"
msgid "Okilinī hi sapat­taṅ­gā­rokiri,"
msgstr "A sweltering woman scattered coals on a co-wife,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:182.4"
msgid "Sīsacchinno ahu coraghātako."
msgstr "A beheaded man was an executioner."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="178"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.711" href="#ms.711"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:183.1"
msgid "Bhikkhu bhikkhunī sikkhamānā,"
msgstr "A monk, a nun, a trainee nun,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:183.2"
msgid "Sāmaṇero atha sāmaṇerikā;"
msgstr "A novice monk, then a novice nun;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:183.3"
msgid "Kassapassa vinayasmiṃ pabbajaṃ,"
msgstr "These having gone forth in the training of Kassapa"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:183.4"
msgid "Pāpakam­ma­makariṃsu tāvade."
msgstr "Did bad deeds just then."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="179"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.712" href="#ms.712"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:184.1"
msgid "Tapodā rājagahe yuddhaṃ,"
msgstr "The Tapodā in Rājagaha, battle,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:184.2"
msgid "nāgānogāhanena ca;"
msgstr "And with the plunging in of elephants;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:184.3"
msgid "Sobhito arahaṃ bhikkhu,"
msgstr "The perfected monk Sobhita"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:184.4"
msgid "pañca­kap­pasataṃ sareti."
msgstr "Recalls five hundred eons."

#. </p></div><h3>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:185.1"
msgid "4.2. Vinītavatthu"
msgstr "Case details, part 1"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="180"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="Bu-Pj.4.8"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.8.1" href="#Bu-Pj.4.8.1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.173" href="#bd.1.173"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.713" href="#ms.713"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:186.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu adhimānena aññaṃ byākāsi."
msgstr "At one time a monk declared final knowledge because of overestimation."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:186.2"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi—"
msgstr "He became remorseful, thinking,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:186.3"
msgid "“bhagavatā sikkhāpadaṃ paññattaṃ."
msgstr "“The Master has laid down a training rule."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:186.4"
msgid "Kacci nu kho ahaṃ pārājikaṃ āpattiṃ āpanno”ti?"
msgstr "Could it be that I’ve committed an offense entailing expulsion?”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:186.5"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "He informed the Master."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:186.6"
msgid "“Anāpatti, bhikkhu, adhimānenā”ti."
msgstr "“There’s no offense for one who overestimates himself.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:186.7"
msgid "(1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="181"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.8.2" href="#Bu-Pj.4.8.2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.714" href="#ms.714"></a><a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.101" href="#Vin.3.101"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu paṇidhāya araññe viharati—"
msgstr "At one time a monk lived in the wilderness"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.2"
msgid "“evaṃ maṃ jano sambhāvessatī”ti."
msgstr "because he wanted people to esteem him."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.3"
msgid "Taṃ jano sambhāvesi."
msgstr "People esteemed him."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.4"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.5"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa."
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion."

#. <strong class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.6"
msgid "Na ca, bhikkhave, paṇidhāya araññe vatthabbaṃ."
msgstr "But, monks, you should not live in the wilderness because of a wish."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.7"
msgid "Yo vaseyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti."
msgstr "If you do, you commit an offense of wrong conduct.”"

#. </strong> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:187.8"
msgid "(2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="182"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.715" href="#ms.715"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu paṇidhāya piṇḍāya carati—"
msgstr "At one time a monk was walking for almsfood"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.2"
msgid "“evaṃ maṃ jano sambhāvessatī”ti."
msgstr "because he wanted people to esteem him."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.3"
msgid "Taṃ jano sambhāvesi."
msgstr "People esteemed him."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.4"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
msgstr "He became remorseful …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.5"
msgid "“anāpatti, bhikkhu, pārājikassa."
msgstr "“There’s no offense entailing expulsion."

#. <strong class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.6"
msgid "Na ca, bhikkhave, paṇidhāya piṇḍāya caritabbaṃ."
msgstr "But, monks, you should not walk for almsfood because of a wish."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.7"
msgid "Yo careyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā”ti."
msgstr "If you do, you commit an offense of wrong conduct.”"

#. </strong> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:188.8"
msgid "(3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="183"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.8.3" href="#Bu-Pj.4.8.3"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.716" href="#ms.716"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:189.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "At one time a monk said to another monk,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:189.2"
msgid "“ye, āvuso, amhākaṃ upajjhāyassa saddhivihārikā sabbeva arahanto”ti."
msgstr "“Those who are pupils of our preceptor are all perfected ones.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:189.3"
msgid "Tassa kukkuccaṃ ahosi … pe …"
