msgid "esā, bhikkhave, itthī kāliṅgassa rañño aggamahesī ahosi."
msgstr "“… That woman, monks, was the chief queen of the King of Kāliṅga."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:232.4"
msgid "Sā issāpakatā sapattiṃ aṅgārakaṭāhena okiri … pe …."
msgstr "Because of jealousy, she threw out her rival and poured a pan of burning coals over her. …”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:232.5"
msgid "(50)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="227"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.187" href="#bd.1.187"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.760" href="#ms.760"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:233.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ asīsakaṃ kabandhaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ."
msgstr "“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw the headless trunk of a body flying through the air,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:233.2"
msgid "Tassa ure akkhīni ceva honti mukhañca."
msgstr "with eyes and mouth on its chest."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:233.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti vibhajjenti."
msgstr "Vultures, crows, and hawks were in close pursuit of it, tearing at it and pulling it to pieces,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:233.4"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "while it uttered cries of distress. …” …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:233.5"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe hāriko nāma coraghātako ahosi … pe …."
msgstr "“… That being, monks, was an executioner called Hārika in this very Rājagaha. …”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:233.6"
msgid "(51)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="228"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.761" href="#ms.761"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:234.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ bhikkhuṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ."
msgstr "“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a monk flying through the air."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:234.2"
msgid "Tassa saṅghāṭipi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā, pattopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto, kāya­bandha­nampi ādittaṃ sampajjalitaṃ sajotibhūtaṃ, kāyopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto."
msgstr "His outer robe was ablaze and burning, as were his bowl, his waistband, and his body."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:234.3"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "He uttered cries of distress. …” …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:234.4"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kassapassa sammā­sambud­dhassa pāvacane pāpabhikkhu ahosi … pe …."
msgstr "“… During the time of the Buddha Kassapa’s dispensation, that monk was a bad monk.” …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:234.5"
msgid "(52)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="229"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.762" href="#ms.762"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ bhikkhuniṃ …"
msgstr "“As I was coming down from Mount Vulture Peak, I saw a nun …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.2"
msgid "addasaṃ sikkhamānaṃ …"
msgstr "I saw a trainee nun …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.3"
msgid "addasaṃ sāmaṇeraṃ …"
msgstr "I saw a novice monk …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.4"
msgid "addasaṃ sāmaṇeriṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantiṃ."
msgstr "I saw a novice nun flying through the air."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.5"
msgid "Tassā saṅghāṭipi ādittā sampajjalitā sajotibhūtā, pattopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto, kāya­bandha­nampi ādittaṃ sampajjalitaṃ sajotibhūtaṃ, kāyopi āditto sampajjalito sajotibhūto."
msgstr "Her outer robe was ablaze and burning, as were her bowl, her waistband, and her body."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.6"
msgid "Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti."
msgstr "She uttered cries of distress."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.7"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi—"
msgstr "And I thought"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.8"
msgid "‘acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho, evarūpopi nāma satto bhavissati."
msgstr "how amazing and astonishing it is that such a being should exist,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.9"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma yakkho bhavissati."
msgstr "such a spirit,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.10"
msgid "Evarūpopi nāma atta­bhāvap­paṭi­lābho bhavissatī’”ti."
msgstr "such a state of existence.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.11"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:235.12"
msgid "“uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "“Venerable Moggallāna is claiming a super-human ability.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="230"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.763" href="#ms.763"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "The Master then said to them:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.188" href="#bd.1.188"></a><a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.108" href="#Vin.3.108"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.2"
msgid "“cakkhubhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti."
msgstr "“There are disciples who possess vision"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.3"
msgid "Ñāṇabhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti."
msgstr "and knowledge,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.4"
msgid "Yatra hi nāma sāvako evarūpaṃ ñassati vā dakkhati vā sakkhiṃ vā karissati."
msgstr "and they can see, know, and witness such things."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.5"
msgid "Pubbeva me sā, bhikkhave, sāmaṇerī diṭṭhā ahosi."
msgstr "I too, monks, have seen this novice nun,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.6"
msgid "Api cāhaṃ na byākāsiṃ."
msgstr "but I didn’t speak about it."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.7"
msgid "Ahañcetaṃ byākareyyaṃ pare ca me na saddaheyyuṃ."
msgstr "If I had, others wouldn’t have believed me,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.8"
msgid "Ye me na saddaheyyuṃ tesaṃ taṃ assa dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr "and that would have been for their harm and suffering for a long time."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.9"
msgid "Esā, bhikkhave, sāmaṇerī kassapassa sammā­sambud­dhassa pāvacane pāpasāmaṇerī ahosi."
msgstr "During the time of Buddha Kassapa’s dispensation, that novice nun was a bad novice nun."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.10"
msgid "Sā tassa kammassa vipākena bahūni vassāni bahūni vassasatāni bahūni vassasahassāni bahūni vassa­sata­sahas­sāni niraye paccitvā"
msgstr "As a result of her deeds, she was tormented in hell for many years, for many hundreds of years, for many thousands of years, for many hundreds of thousands of years."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.11"
msgid "tasseva kammassa vipākāvasesena evarūpaṃ atta­bhāvap­paṭi­lābhaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr "And now, because of the remaining result of her actions, she’s experiencing such an existence."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.12"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.13"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:236.14"
msgid "(53–‍56)"
msgstr ""

#. </p></div><hr><p><a class="sc" id="231"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.9.4" href="#Bu-Pj.4.9.4"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.764" href="#ms.764"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said to the monks,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.2"
msgid "“yatāyaṃ, āvuso, tapodā sandati so daho acchodako sītodako sātodako setako suppatittho ramaṇīyo pahūta­maccha­kacchapo cakkamattāni ca padumāni pupphantī”ti."
msgstr "“This stream, the Tapodā, flows from a lake with beautiful waters—cool, sweat, and pure—with smooth and pleasant banks, with an abundance of fish and turtles, and with blooming lotuses the size of wheels.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.4"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā mahāmoggallāno evaṃ vakkhati—"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Mahāmoggallāna say"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.5"
msgid "‘yatāyaṃ, āvuso, tapodā sandati so daho acchodako sītodako sātodako setako suppatittho ramaṇīyo pahūta­maccha­kacchapo cakkamattāni ca padumāni pupphantī’ti."
msgstr "such a thing?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.6"
msgid "Atha ca panāyaṃ tapodā kuthitā sandati."
msgstr "On the the contrary, the Tapodā is hot."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.7"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna is claiming a super-human ability.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.8"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "And they informed the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.9"
msgid "“Yatāyaṃ, bhikkhave, tapodā sandati so daho acchodako sītodako sātodako setako suppatittho ramaṇīyo pahūta­maccha­kacchapo cakkamattāni ca padumāni pupphanti."
msgstr "“Monks, the Tapodā flows from a lake of beautiful waters—with smooth and pleasant banks, with an abundance of fish and turtles, and with blooming lotuses the size of wheels."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.10"
msgid "Api cāyaṃ, bhikkhave, tapodā dvinnaṃ mahānirayānaṃ antarikāya āgacchati."
msgstr "But the Tapodā runs between the two great hells;"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.189" href="#bd.1.189"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.11"
msgid "Tenāyaṃ tapodā kuthitā sandati."
msgstr "that’s why it’s hot."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.12"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.13"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:237.14"
msgid "(57)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="232"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.9.5" href="#Bu-Pj.4.9.5"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.765" href="#ms.765"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena rājā māgadho seniyo bimbisāro licchavīhi saddhiṃ saṅgāmento pabhaggo ahosi."
msgstr "At one time King Seniya Bimbisāra of Magadha was defeated in battle by the Licchavīs."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.2"
msgid "Atha rājā pacchā senaṃ saṅkaḍḍhitvā licchavayo parājesi."
msgstr "The King then rallied his army and beat the Licchavīs."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.3"
msgid "Saṅgāme ca nandī carati—"
msgstr "People were delighted and the word spread:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.4"
msgid "“raññā licchavī pabhaggā”ti."
msgstr "“The Licchavīs have been defeated by the king!”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.5"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said to the monks:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.6"
msgid "“rājā, āvuso, licchavīhi pabhaggo”ti."
msgstr "“The King was defeated by the Licchavīs.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.7"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.8"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā mahāmoggallāno evaṃ vakkhati—"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Moggallāna say"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.9"
msgid "‘rājā, āvuso, licchavīhi pabhaggo’ti."
msgstr "that the King was defeated by the Licchavīs"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.10"
msgid "Saṅgāme ca nandī carati—"
msgstr "when people are delighted"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.11"
msgid "‘raññā licchavī pabhaggā’ti."
msgstr "and the word is spreading that the Licchavīs have been defeated by the King?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.12"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna is claiming a super-human ability.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.13"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They informed the Master."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.109" href="#Vin.3.109"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.14"
msgid "“Paṭhamaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā licchavīhi pabhaggo."
msgstr "“Monks, first the King was defeated by the Licchavīs,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.15"
msgid "Atha rājā pacchā senaṃ saṅkaḍḍhitvā licchavayo parājesi."
msgstr "but then, after he had rallied his army, the King beat the Licchavīs."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.16"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.17"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:238.18"
msgid "(58)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="233"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.9.6" href="#Bu-Pj.4.9.6"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.766" href="#ms.766"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Mahāmoggallāna said to the monks:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.2"
msgid "“idhāhaṃ, āvuso, sappinikāya nadiyā tīre āneñjaṃ samādhiṃ samāpanno nāgānaṃ ogayha uttarantānaṃ koñcaṃ karontānaṃ saddaṃ assosin”ti."
msgstr "“After attaining an imperturbable stillness on the banks of the river Sappinikā, I heard the noise of elephants plunging in, emerging, and trumpeting.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him:"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.190" href="#bd.1.190"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.4"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā mahāmoggallāno āneñjaṃ samādhiṃ samāpanno saddaṃ sossati."
msgstr "“How can Venerable Mahāmoggallāna say such a thing?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.5"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "He’s claiming a super-human ability.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.6"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They informed the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.7"
msgid "“Attheso, bhikkhave, samādhi so ca kho aparisuddho."
msgstr "“Monks, there is such a stillness, but itʼs not wholly purified."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.8"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, moggallāno āha."
msgstr "Moggallāna spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.9"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, moggallānassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Moggallāna.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:239.10"
msgid "(59)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="234"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="Bu-Pj.4.9.7" href="#Bu-Pj.4.9.7"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.767" href="#ms.767"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā sobhito bhikkhū āmantesi—"
msgstr "Venerable Sobhita said to the monks,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.2"
msgid "“ahaṃ, āvuso, pañca kappasatāni anussarāmī”ti."
msgstr "“I can recall five hundred eons.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "The monks complained and criticized him:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.4"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma āyasmā sobhito evaṃ vakkhati—"
msgstr "“How can Venerable Sobhita say"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.5"
msgid "‘ahaṃ, āvuso, pañca kappasatāni anussarāmī’ti."
msgstr "that he can recall five hundred eons?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.6"
msgid "Uttari­manus­sa­dhammaṃ āyasmā sobhito ullapatī”ti."
msgstr "He’s claiming a super-human ability.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.7"
msgid "Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "They informed the Master."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.8"
msgid "“Atthesā, bhikkhave, sobhitassa."
msgstr "“Monks, Sobhita has this ability,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.9"
msgid "Sā ca kho ekāyeva jāti."
msgstr "and that was just one birth."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.10"
msgid "Saccaṃ, bhikkhave, sobhito āha."
msgstr "Sobhita spoke truthfully."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.11"
msgid "Anāpatti, bhikkhave, sobhitassā”ti."
msgstr "There’s no offense for Sobhita.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:240.12"
msgid "(60)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="235"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.768" href="#ms.768"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:241.1"
msgid "Catut­tha­pā­rāji­kaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The fourth offense entailing expulsion is finished."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="236"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.769" href="#ms.769"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.1"
msgid "Uddiṭṭhā kho āyasmanto cattāro pārājikā dhammā,"
msgstr "“Venerables, the four rules entailing expulsion have been recited."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.2"
msgid "yesaṃ bhikkhu aññataraṃ vā aññataraṃ vā āpajjitvā na labhati bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ,"
msgstr "If a monk commits any one of them, he is no longer in communion with the monks."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.3"
msgid "yathā pure tathā pacchā, pārājiko hoti asaṃvāso."
msgstr "As before, so after, he’s expelled and not in communion."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.4"
msgid "Tatthāyasmante pucchāmi—"
msgstr "In regard to this I ask you,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.5"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.6"
msgid "Dutiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A second time I ask,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.7"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.8"
msgid "Tatiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A third time I ask,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.9"
msgid "“kaccittha parisuddhā”?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.10"
msgid "Pari­sud­dhet­thā­yasmanto, tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "You are pure in this and therefore silent."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:242.11"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmīti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.”"

#. </p><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="237"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.770" href="#ms.770"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:243.1"
msgid "Pārājikaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The rules entailing expulsion are finished."

#. </p><p class="endsection summary"><a class="sc" id="238"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.771" href="#ms.771"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:244.1"
msgid "Tassuddānaṃ"
msgstr "This is the summary:"

#. </p><div class="uddana"><p><a class="sc" id="239"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.772" href="#ms.772"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:245.1"
msgid "Methu­nādinnā­dānañca,"
msgstr "Sexual intercourse, and stealing,"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:245.2"
msgid "­manus­sa­vigga­huttari;"
msgstr "Person, super;"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:245.3"
msgid "Pārājikāni cattāri,"
msgstr "The four offenses entailing expulsion—"

#. <br> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:245.4"
msgid "chejjavatthū asaṃsayāti."
msgstr "The foundation is definitively cut off."

#. </p></div><p class="endsection"><a class="sc" id="240"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.773" href="#ms.773"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj4:246.1"
msgid "Pārājikakaṇḍaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The chapter on offenses entailing expulsion is finished."

